         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_3edc396b22f787340a5a2130f3c77ba9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of scrapbooks and photostats of correspondence and clippings documenting the purchase of James Boswell's private papers by Yale University.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
